This is a tool to automatically generate static images from 3d models.

It compiles and runs in Ubuntu.

=====
The following libraries are required:
=====

1. Build environment, python, gcc, scons, etc.

%apt-get install scons

2. libassimp 

%apt-get install libassimp-dev

3. libMagicWand 

%apt-get install libmagickwand-dev

4. libOpenCV 

%apt-get install libopencv-dev

5. libOpenCV-nonfree 

%apt-get install software-properties-common
%add-apt-repository --yes ppa:xqms/opencv-nonfree
%apt-get update
%apt-get install libopencv-nonfree-dev

=====
To compile the code
=====

1. Release mode:
scons 

2. Debug mode:
scons type=debug